Interface Device.Listener

      • parameterUpdated

        void parameterUpdated(Device device,
                      Device.Value value)
        Called whenever a UE parameter value changes.
        Parameters:
        device - device instance whose value changed.
        value - changed parameter value.

      • parameterBlockUpdated

        void parameterBlockUpdated(Device device,
                           int id,
                           java.util.List<Device.Value> values)
        Called whenever a table style parameter on the UE changes. Table style parameters are a collection of array type values. A good example of table style parameter is UMTS monitored list, which contains information about monitored cells, so it would hold arrays of parameters such as PSC, EcNo, RSCP, etc. Each array in table is guaranteed to contain same number of items, and items on same index can be considered to form a row on a table.
        Parameters:
        device - device instance whose value changed.
        id - parameter ID of the table style parameter.
        values - list of array type parameters that form the rows of the table.

      • stateUpdated

        void stateUpdated(Device device,
                  int id,
                  int state)
        Called whenever the state of the UI changes, ie. for example call is activated.
        Parameters:
        device - device instance whose state changed.
        id - state change type. Types defined in Device.StateMessages class.
        state - current state of the device. States defined in Device.DeviceStates class.

      • scriptStatus

        void scriptStatus(Device device,
                  int state,
                  int progress,
                  java.lang.String text)
        Called whenever the script progress on UE changes.
        Parameters:
        device - device instance whose script updated.
        state - current state of the script. States defined in Device.ScriptStates class.
        progress - progress in percentage.
        text - textual description of the current state.

      • eventUpdate

        void eventUpdate(Device device,
                 int id,
                 java.lang.String description,
                 java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> args)
        Called whenever there is an event update on the UE.
        Parameters:
        device - device instance that produced the event.
        id - event ID. IDs defined in Events class.
        description - Textual description, usually empty.
        args - List of arguments related to the event.

      • testResult

        uplink - true if uplink test.
        statistics - statistical values related to the result.
